data.description: Newly Built Charm: Experience the comforts of modern living with this 3-bed, 2-bath home in Cleburne, TX. Enjoy a well-thought-out split bedroom floorplan, designed for utmost convenience. Step inside to an expansive living area featuring stained concrete flooring and open to a sophisticated kitchen, equipped with granite countertops, stainless appliances, and stylish cabinet underlighting. Relish in the abundant space afforded by a separate laundry room. Retreat to a primary bedroom outfitted with an en suite that boasts a large walk-in shower, dual sinks, and a roomy closet. On the exterior, admire the home's distinctive board and batten siding complemented by brick accents, as well as a gorgeous covered front porch with rustic cedar posts. The backyard, graced by a storage building and a 6-foot wooden privacy fence, completes this picture of suburban elegance. Contact the listing agent now for an exclusive showing!
